meanings.definition: Not included in a list or directory.
meanings.sent1: The secret treasure map was hidden in an unlisted location.
meanings.sent2: Her phone number is unlisted, so I couldn't find it in the phone book.
meanings.sent3: The unlisted ingredients in the recipe turned out to be a surprising twist.
meanings.sent4: His unlisted talents finally came to light during the school talent show.
meanings.sent5: The unlisted items on the menu were revealed as special treats for regular customers.

meanings.definition: Not published or made available to the public.
meanings.sent1: The unlisted manuscript was a hidden gem waiting to be discovered.
meanings.sent2: The unlisted movie premiere was attended by only a select few.
meanings.sent3: The unlisted concert was so exclusive that even the birds couldn't get tickets.
meanings.sent4: Her unlisted diary held all her deepest thoughts and dreams.
meanings.sent5: The unlisted art exhibition showcased rare pieces never seen before.
